Package it.polimi.se2019.model.board

Class Tile

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2019.model.board.Tile
  • public class Tile
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains all information needed for a Tile, a single part of a board. It supports grabbing AmmoCard or Weapon.
